{"tid":1690803,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人！反抗！！！","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:08:45.000Z","uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fdaceb9b1abdd86221e94808fc9c2f6607403079","tid":1690803,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"運動經過咗四個多月，口號由<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span></span> 演變到 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人反抗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際行動，香港人又進化咗幾多呢？一齊望下：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>和理非系</ins><br />\n摺紙：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n連儱牆文宣：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n唱歌：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n屌狗：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n罷工：<span style=\"color: blue;\">失敗</span><br />\n罷鐵：<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">局部失敗</span><br />\n起底：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n阻狗：<span style=\"color: blue;\">失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>勇武系</ins><br />\n路障放火：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n裝修：<span style=\"color: orange;\">持續</span><br />\n打狗：<span style=\"color: violet;\">零聲</span><br />\n攻狗陣：<span style=\"color: red;\">已成絕響</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非係勇武的盾，當勇武要撤退，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非唔應該讓路畀狗行</span>。<br />\n眼見太多次和理非係狗衝入人群時讓路，呢啲情況通常都好迫人，勇武焗住畀人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再集中屌狗啦</span>，一來佢地不痛不癢，二來畀佢地有防備。要攻其不備先係上策。<br />\n人數多的情況下（講緊三倍以上），唔該就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">屌佢地係無意義的行為（唔排除佢地已經慣咗）</span></span>，我地向佢地發洩完轉頭佢地就會十倍奉還畀唔好彩畀人捉到既手足，凡事三思而後行啊。"},{"pid":"cebc63274b5b323f60435bd8df89129d7af5e1f1","tid":1690803,"uid":275730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"對準政權, 首先打擊香港經濟"},{"pid":"3c9559e9517ff9eb8321b88df126d2f66aa0f86a","tid":1690803,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cebc63274b5b323f60435bd8df89129d7af5e1f1","tid":1690803,"uid":275730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"對準政權, 首先打擊香港經濟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"無人理就算啦<br />\n<br />\n係啊，打擊經濟戰啊？！<br />\n又睇下香港人捱到雙十一集運幾多囉<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，話自己黃果堆過半數都係淘寶撚嚟"}]}